          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780394741048" href="/book/show/539477.Letters_to_a_Young_Poet">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/614778-ahmad-sharabiani?shelf=literature">literature</a>, 
