<div id="review_115407803" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/115407803" />
    <a title="Evan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1248986-evan"><img alt="Evan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1488574589p2/1248986.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/115407803?book_show_action=true">Aug 05, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Evan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Evan" href="/user/show/1248986-evan">Evan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780394741048" href="/book/show/539477.Letters_to_a_Young_Poet">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=poetry">poetry</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=essay-critique-short-form-or-memoir">essay-critique-short-form-or-memoir</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=my-faves">my-faves</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=2010-reads">2010-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=__in-my-collection">__in-my-collection</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=epistle-larry-approves">epistle-larry-approves</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1248986-evan?shelf=philosophy">philosophy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer115407803" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12756483493663330544"><br/>Sigh. Rilke answers nothing and answers everything.<br/><br/>He talks of our ancestors as being &quot;murmuring blood.&quot; This book, containing the voice of his wisdom across the age, is blood that courses through us and speaks.<br/><br/>It offers comfort to me in the face of life&apos;s challenges, its unrequited longings. It helps me see the value of difficulties and the importance of patience.<br/><br/>I wish I&apos;d read this many years ago. I think it would have given me guidance I needed, even if it didn&apos;t lead me away from mistakes. </span>
  <span id="freeText12756483493663330544" style="display:none"><br />Sigh. Rilke answers nothing and answers everything.<br /><br />He talks of our ancestors as being "murmuring blood." This book, containing the voice of his wisdom across the age, is blood that courses through us and speaks.<br /><br />It offers comfort to me in the face of life's challenges, its unrequited longings. It helps me see the value of difficulties and the importance of patience.<br /><br />I wish I'd read this many years ago. I think it would have given me guidance I needed, even if it didn't lead me away from mistakes. Rilke knows the mistakes are essential.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12756483493663330544" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


